oh=00_AYCUmaBgBvFdbdJrJxUi73FshnOeTqSb6Tg6AcG7beFdHA&oe=67519DD1"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "NITT_DigitalAssets_v05_HDvideo_1920x1080.png", "id": "942459706719818", "uri": "https://scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035433_942459710053151_7882200148446536338_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=n3nTsIa_Zo4Q7kNvgEtWJCf&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYChpbiX9ytyM6NnX6UYbffgKDlb7BwMX9xLNih2k6SIMA&oe=67519445"}, "display_name": "MLK: Now is the Time", "keywords": ["civil", "rights", "dream"], "long_description": "** WINNER: Audience Award: 2023 SXSW XR Experience Spotlight \n** WINNER: AIXR: 2023 Social Impact Award\n** WINNER:  Webby: 2024 AI, Metaverse & Virtual: Public Service & Activism\n** WINNER:  Webby People's Voice: 2024 AI, Metaverse & Virtual: Public Service & Activism\n** WINNER:  Games For Change: Best in XR\n** NOMINEE: Emmy: 2023 Outstanding Emerging Media Program\n** NOMINEE: 2024 Producers Guild Awards: Innovation Award\n\nIt\u2019s been sixty years since Dr. Martin Luther King delivered his iconic \"I Have a Dream\" speech, but the messages from that speech resonate today.  \n \n\u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d is an immersive journey that explores key themes of Dr. King's speech and highlights systemic inequities that persist in our society. Through first-person stories and interactions, \u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d drops you into a thoroughly modern interpretation of a contemporary March on Washington that will inform and inspire a new generation of activists. ", "short_description": "Dr. Martin Luther King's iconic \"I Have a Dream\" speech contains messages that still resonate today, sixty years later.  \n \n\u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d is an immersive journey that explores key themes of Dr. King's speech and highlights systemic inequities that persist in our society. Through first-person stories and interactions, \u201cMLK: Now is the Time\u201d drops you into a thoroughly modern interpretation of a contemporary March on Washington that will inform and inspire a new generation of activists."}]}, "developer_name": "Flight School Studio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://nowisthetime.time.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "TIME Immersive", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://time.com/nowisthetime/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "DOCUMENTARY_HISTORY", "EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8686521271437636"}, "review_messages": ["", "I did not see any changes, or see any notes so pushing this back to the developer. They can make any changes necessary and resubmit when ready. "]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223477_6076997912344657_4165052289897781929_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=A0FQ4HyzmxEQ7kNvgGt0MEI&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCq6a0Yz4P7FZTfubt70RJoWAKD-0-9WxnL7PqGK_x_bw&oe=6751A95D"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "MLK: Now is the Time", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "APPS", "id": "362692211442873"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Media", "id": "434961926215971"}], "release_date